      "side": 1,
      "message": "It is a shame we still need all the if(alphaOnly) { swizzle(\"aaaa\"); } stuff throughout the code. I wonder if there is any easy way to have all that logic be in SkSL. Right now I think it is a little fragile since if we add new code that wants to sample textures it needs to remember to put in this special check and swizzle change.\n\nBut as of now I think this is probably the best we can do.",
      "revId": "a12bf1f7e24bed0654d2d5126b2bfd892da7196a",
